</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-esp-invoice-due-dates.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-esp-invoice-due-dates.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-esp-invoice-due-dates.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Period interval</strong> field, select the period interval type:</p>
<ul sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-esp-invoice-due-dates.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">
